#: ../../source/production/observability/metrics.rst:4
msgid "Metrics Reference"
msgstr "指标参考"

#: ../../source/production/observability/metrics.rst:6
msgid ""
"LMCache provides comprehensive metrics via Prometheus to help you monitor"
" performance, cache efficiency, and system health. These metrics are "
"exposed via the vLLM ``/metrics`` endpoint when LMCache is integrated "
"with vLLM, or via the LMCache internal API server."
msgstr "LMCache 通过 Prometheus 提供全面的指标，以帮助您监控性能、缓存效率和系统健康。这些指标在 LMCache 与 vLLM 集成时通过 vLLM ``/metrics`` 端点公开，或者通过 LMCache 内部 API 服务器公开。"

